  <span id="freeText13259145415611649221" style="display:none">If there were ever the opportunity to recreate original sin, this may be how it would turn out. <br /><br />Showdown starts out enigmatic, and continues to keep you guessing through to the end. There were times I had to walk away,thinking "how can things get any worse!", but was always drawn back to find out what happened next.<br /><br />Read the Circle Trilogy first. Thomas Hunter comes into this story line and you will appreciate the background.<br /><br />Ted has given us a fantastic story where many what-ifs of mankind and christianity are explored. <br /><br />This would make a tremendous movie!<br /></span>
