<span id="freeTextContainer18121549908415094978">All I can say is wow. This went from me being thoroughly confused in the beginning, to loving every word through the middle, to me feeling OK with the ending. Was the ending bad? No, but it was very predictable. I will say that this book is very unique and unlike other books I have read! I’m so exciting to read the next book!</span>

